description: Smooth Commander Pepes is the third collection from Nakamotos on Bitcoin. This collection is a collaboration the OG Rare Pepe artist ayaLAN who created the coveted HairPepe. Continuing the Nakamotos on Bitcoin tradition of collections paying homage to the OG Bitcoiners, the Smooth Commander Pepe is created in a similar template of the OG Rare Pepe NFT's with the styling of the original HairPepe.
name: Smooth Commander Pepes
